        },
        "caption": "8 and 2 make 10."
      }
    },
    {
      "problem": "7 and 3 — what whole do they make?",
      "steps": [
        "Join the two parts.",
        "7 and 3 more.",
        "Count on: eight, nine, ten.",
        "They make 10."
      ],
      "answer": "10"
    }
  ],
